reviews.review_text: What No Reviews??? What an honor to jump in and be the first to review.  Yes Philly has a long tradition of barn burners, this is no exception!  And the quality of this recording is superb.  The review threads of other versions pine for a sweet SBD, well here you go!  Charlie Miller - making (an already awesome) Archive better - one show at a time!
Thank you Have a nice day 😊 🙏🏼
